Baby/Child Dedication||<p>Dedicating your child to God is a very important step in the life of a family. &nbsp;We are excited to participate in this important step in the life of your family.</p>
<p><a href="/child-dedications/">If you would like more information about our Dedication Services click here &gt;&gt;</a></p>
<p>You must participate in an informational and connecting meeting with Pastor Linda Noah on Sunday May 1 at 9:15 AM in Room 227 (Small Conference Room) in order for your family to participate in the dedication event the following Sunday. Please fill out the <a target="_blank" href="http://f049e6c6bc51d6086828-1f3d9bf827f6f62072870f1ea348709c.r40.cf2.rackcdn.com/uploaded/c/0e744573_child-dedication-form.pdf">Baby Dedication Form</a> so that we can prepare for your family. Please submit the form along with a photo of your child (or family) prior to the class on May 1.</p>
